{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"As an artist,"},{"time":2000,"text":"connection is very important to me."},{"time":4000,"text":"Through my work I'm trying to articulate"},{"time":7000,"text":"that humans are not separate from nature"},{"time":10000,"text":"and that everything is interconnected."},{"time":14000,"text":"I first went to Antarctica almost 10 years ago,"},{"time":16000,"text":"where I saw my first icebergs."},{"time":18000,"text":"I was in awe."},{"time":21000,"text":"My heart beat fast, my head was dizzy,"},{"time":24000,"text":"trying to comprehend what it was that stood in front of me."},{"time":27000,"text":"The icebergs around me"},{"time":29000,"text":"were almost 200 feet out of the water,"},{"time":32000,"text":"and I could only help but wonder"},{"time":34000,"text":"that this was one snowflake"},{"time":36000,"text":"on top of another snowflake,"},{"time":38000,"text":"year after year."}]},{"cues":[{"time":40000,"text":"Icebergs are born"},{"time":42000,"text":"when they calve off of glaciers"},{"time":45000,"text":"or break off of ice shelves."},{"time":50000,"text":"Each iceberg has its own individual personality."},{"time":54000,"text":"They have a distinct way"},{"time":56000,"text":"of interacting with their environment"},{"time":58000,"text":"and their experiences."},{"time":61000,"text":"Some refuse to give up"},{"time":63000,"text":"and hold on to the bitter end,"},{"time":65000,"text":"while others can't take it anymore"},{"time":67000,"text":"and crumble in a fit of dramatic passion."}]},{"cues":[{"time":71000,"text":"It's easy to think, when you look at an iceberg,"},{"time":74000,"text":"that they're isolated,"},{"time":76000,"text":"that they're separate and alone,"},{"time":78000,"text":"much like we as humans sometimes view ourselves."},{"time":81000,"text":"But the reality is far from it."},{"time":83000,"text":"As an iceberg melts,"},{"time":85000,"text":"I am breathing in"},{"time":87000,"text":"its ancient atmosphere."},{"time":89000,"text":"As the iceberg melts,"},{"time":91000,"text":"it is releasing mineral-rich fresh water"},{"time":95000,"text":"that nourishes many forms of life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":99000,"text":"I approach photographing these icebergs"},{"time":102000,"text":"as if I'm making portraits of my ancestors,"},{"time":105000,"text":"knowing that in these individual moments"},{"time":108000,"text":"they exist in that way"},{"time":110000,"text":"and will never exist that way again."},{"time":112000,"text":"It is not a death when they melt;"},{"time":114000,"text":"it is not an end,"},{"time":116000,"text":"but a continuation"},{"time":118000,"text":"of their path through the cycle of life."},{"time":126000,"text":"Some of the ice in the icebergs that I photograph is very young --"},{"time":130000,"text":"a couple thousand years old."},{"time":132000,"text":"And some of the ice"},{"time":134000,"text":"is over 100,000 years old."}]},{"cues":[{"time":146000,"text":"The last pictures I'd like to show you"},{"time":148000,"text":"are of an iceberg that I photographed"},{"time":150000,"text":"in Qeqetarsuaq, Greenland."},{"time":153000,"text":"It's a very rare occasion"},{"time":155000,"text":"that you get to actually witness"},{"time":157000,"text":"an iceberg rolling."},{"time":159000,"text":"So here it is."},{"time":161000,"text":"You can see on the left side a small boat."},{"time":164000,"text":"That's about a 15-foot boat."},{"time":167000,"text":"And I'd like you to pay attention"},{"time":169000,"text":"to the shape of the iceberg"},{"time":171000,"text":"and where it is at the waterline."},{"time":174000,"text":"You can see here, it begins to roll,"},{"time":176000,"text":"and the boat has moved to the other side, and the man is standing there."},{"time":178000,"text":"This is an average-size Greenlandic iceberg."},{"time":181000,"text":"It's about 120 feet above the water,"},{"time":184000,"text":"or 40 meters."},{"time":186000,"text":"And this video is real time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":188000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":217000,"text":"And just like that,"},{"time":219000,"text":"the iceberg shows you a different side of its personality."}]},{"cues":[{"time":223000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":225000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}